name: babygenderrevealboy
0:
”Alexa, tell baby gender”
”Alexa, open baby gender”
”Alexa, ask baby gender to reveal gender”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby gender
des: This skill can be used at baby gender reveal party. This skill is for Baby Boy. For Baby Girl, you can add "baby gender reveal girl". But don't add both the skills at the same time, as both use the same skill invocation name. This skill is specifically designed to reveal baby boy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
